  <brief_title>HYSTERIA Evaluation of Clinical HYpnosis After Surgical Resection for Crohn Disease on Post-operative Analgesia</brief_title>
  <acronym>HYSTERIA</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Study Evaluating the Effect of Pre-operative Hypnosis on Anesthesia, Analgesia and Perioperative Stress Laparoscopic Ileo-caecal Resections of Crohn's Disease.</official_title>
