  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study will be to show a decrease in postoperative morphine consumption by the
      practice of perioperative self-hypnosis in patients undergoing laparoscopic ileo-caecal
      resection for Crohn's disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
